   "source": [
    "## Section 9 — Plotting\n",
    "\n",
    "**Accuracy curve:** Top-1 mean with ±1 std error bars vs subset size. Red dashed line = Phase 1 ceiling. This is the core dissertation figure — shows the performance cliff at small sizes.  \n",
    "\n",
    "**Per-class F1 heatmap:** 5×10 grid (subset sizes × classes), colour-coded green=1.0 → red=0.0. Confirms which classes collapse first under data scarcity — expected to match Phase 1 fragile classes (cat, bird, dog for CIFAR-10)."
